elements.name: SyncPipeline operator MUST NOT return anything DoSync()
nil's are not passed through WiredOperators
SyncPipeline operators MUST NOT ask for flush
SyncPipeline must have only one workpiece  inside
SyncPipeline: one work in -> one item out
On critical errors pipeline must be disassembled immediately
AsyncPipeline: work does not come out, errs only
AsyncPuller: if ctxin.Err() - stop processing stdin/flush
AsyncPuller: if operator returns any error - stop processing stdin/flush
AsyncPuller: check ctxin.Err() all the time
